as the requested size, as it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nVectors"},{"text":" is 0 or the sum of all bytes in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"vectors"},{"text":" is 0).","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"text":" is not ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"partial result will be returned, without an error.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Some implementations of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_output_stream_writev()"},{"type":"text","text":" may have limitations on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"aggregate buffer size, and will return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"invalidArgument"},{"type":"text","text":" if these"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"are exceeded. For example, when writing to a local file on UNIX platforms,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the aggregate buffer size must not exceed "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"G_MAXSSIZE"},{"text":" bytes.","type":"text"}